rows.label: tlk45450112_03_msg0001
rows.name:
When we don't have work to
do for Bahn-sama, Couche
and I talk about dancing.

rows.label: tlk45450112_03_msg0002
rows.name:
We could never have made a living as
dancers back in our hometowns, so we
made the right choice coming here!

rows.label: tlk45450112_03_msg0003
rows.name:
It's lovely to be able to work together
with someone who shares my passion for
dancing. And the pay's great too!
